songs.lyrics:
1. Oh, come, all ye faithful, Joyful and triumphant! Oh, come ye, oh come ye to Bethlehem. Come and behold him, Born the King of angels;

<br>
<br>Oh, come, let us adore him; Oh, come, let us adore him; Oh, come, let us adore him, Christ, the Lord.

<br>
<br>2.- Sing, choirs of angels, Sing in exultation; Sing, all ye citizens of heav'n above! Glory to God, Glory in the highest;

<br>
<br>3. Yea, Lord, we greet thee, Born this happy morning; Jesus, to thee be all glory giv'n. Son of the Father, Now in flesh appearing;
<br>
<br>
